highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 267 weeks straight.
“Sweetest Pie” by Megan Thee Stallion and Dua Lipa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #17.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Lo Siento BB:/ (with Bad Bunny & Julieta Venegas)” is the highest at #27.
“Envolver” by Anitta is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 97 spots at #28.
